main event: Observers reported seeing two spiral-shaped objects in the sky over Blue Point, New York, on multiple nights in October 1966.
interesting points: The objects were described as bright white and very clear,One object appeared to have a green light rotating around its middle,The objects exhibited a zigzag flight pattern,The sighting lasted for about 3 to 5 minutes each night,The objects disappeared instantaneously while moving northward.
witness description: 49-year-old computer technician, experienced observer of aerial phenomena
